<metal:block i18n:domain="schooltool.gradebook">
  <div class="header" i18n:translate="">
    What is This?
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <p i18n:translate="">
      This page allows you to manage the Course Worksheets for this
      course.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
      The templates are created separately and define what activites
      will be on the Course Worksheets.  Use this form to deploy the
      worksheets to the teacher gradebooks of all sections of this
      course for one or more terms.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="">
      You can also hide worksheets if you do not want teachers to see them.
    </p>
  </div>
</metal:block>
